{"tid":1855372,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"老人攔省委書記：外村人不讓進","createTime":"2020-02-01T05:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T05:06:16.000Z","uid":81228,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"42e026e18e5b5bd9264e7fa8e5efe3998f32b222","tid":1855372,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T05:06:16.000Z","msg":"前日下午3時許，江蘇省委書記婁勤儉乘車到南京市江寧區湯山街道葛巷村村口的疫情檢查點時，被數名戴口罩、臂套紅袖章的老人攔住，稱「外村的人不讓進」。婁勤儉問「村裏有發熱（燒）的病人嗎」，老人回答說「沒有！連在外打工的人都沒回來」，並催促婁離開。婁表明身分，並讚「管得嚴是應該的」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b/article/20200201/s00013/1580495372503/%e8%80%81%e4%ba%ba%e6%94%94%e7%9c%81%e5%a7%94%e6%9b%b8%e8%a8%98-%e5%a4%96%e6%9d%91%e4%ba%ba%e4%b8%8d%e8%ae%93%e9%80%b2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%2Farticle%2F20200201%2Fs00013%2F1580495372503%2F%25e8%2580%2581%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%2594%2594%25e7%259c%2581%25e5%25a7%2594%25e6%259b%25b8%25e8%25a8%2598-%25e5%25a4%2596%25e6%259d%2591%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e4%25b8%258d%25e8%25ae%2593%25e9%2580%25b2&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IhVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=c2b83c84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%2Farticle%2F20200201%2Fs00013%2F1580495372503%2F%25e8%2580%2581%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%2594%2594%25e7%259c%2581%25e5%25a7%2594%25e6%259b%25b8%25e8%25a8%2598-%25e5%25a4%2596%25e6%259d%2591%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e4%25b8%258d%25e8%25ae%2593%25e9%2580%25b2&h=2cd72c65\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b/article/20200201/s00013/1580495372503/%e8%80%81%e4%ba%ba%e6%94%94%e7%9c%81%e5%a7%94%e6%9b%b8%e8%a8%98-%e5%a4%96%e6%9d%91%e4%ba%ba%e4%b8%8d%e8%ae%93%e9%80%b2</a>"}]}